CSS:

```
#lightbox {
  display: none;
  position: fixed;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
}

#lightbox-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
}

#lightbox-content {
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
}

#lightbox-prev,
#lightbox-next {
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  font-size: 48px;
  color: #fff;
  cursor: pointer;
  z-index: 100;
}

#lightbox-prev {
  left: 20px;
}

#lightbox-next {
  right: 20px;
}

#lightbox-image {
  max-width: 80%;
  max-height: 80%;
  display: block;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

#lightbox-close {
  position: absolute;
  top: 10px;
  right: 10px;
  font-size: 36px;
  color: #fff;
  cursor: pointer;
  z-index: 100;
}
```

jQuery:

```
$(document).ready(function() {
  var $lightbox = $('#lightbox');
  var $overlay = $('#lightbox-overlay');
  var $image = $('#lightbox-image');
  var $prev = $('#lightbox-prev');
  var $next = $('#lightbox-next');
  var $close = $('#lightbox-close');
  var $links = $('a[data-image]');
  var index = 0;

  function showLightbox() {
    $lightbox.fadeIn();
    $overlay.on('click', hideLightbox);
    $(document).on('keyup', handleKeyup);
  }

  function hideLightbox() {
    $lightbox.fadeOut();
    $overlay.off('click');
    $(document).off('keyup');
  }

  function handleKeyup(e) {
    e.preventDefault();
    if (e.keyCode == 37) { // left arrow
      showPrevImage();
    } else if (e.keyCode == 39) { // right arrow
      showNextImage();
    } else if (e.keyCode == 27) { // escape key
      hideLightbox();
    }
  }

  function showNextImage() {
    index++;
    if (index >= $links.length) {
      index = 0;
    }
    $image.attr('src', $links.eq(index).data('image'));
  }

  function showPrevImage() {
    index--;
    if (index < 0) {
      index = $links.length - 1;
    }
    $image.attr('src', $links.eq(index).data('image'));
  }

  $links.on('click', function(e) {
    e.preventDefault();
    index = $links.index(this);
    $image.attr('src', $(this).data('image'));
    showLightbox();
  });

  $prev.on('click', showPrevImage);
  $next.on('click', showNextImage);
  $close.on('click', hideLightbox);
});
```

Explanation:

The HTML code includes a hidden `div` with an `id` of "lightbox" that will contain the lightbox overlay and content. The content includes a previous button, next button, image element, and close button. The images to be displayed are added as link tags (`<a>`) with a `data-image` attribute that contains the image file path.

The CSS code styles the lightbox and its components. The overlay fills the entire screen and has a semi-transparent black background. The content is centered on the screen and includes the navigation buttons, image, and close button.

The jQuery code defines variables for each of the lightbox components and the list of image links. It also defines functions to show and hide the lightbox, handle key events for navigation and closing, and show the previous and next images.

